Name: AS 1108-C-000(temp)
Note: Attention: Adapter required. The AS100 series sensor has two analogue output channels. these must be split to two analogue channels in on the CSI-C-12. This setting represents the temperature signal on pin 4. Pin 3 GND must be connected to GND pin of CSI-C-12 input channel

Name: AS 1108-C-000(saturation)
Note: Attention: Adapter required. The AS100 series sensor has two analogue output channels. these must be split to two analogue channels in on the CSI-C-12. This setting represents the saturation signal on pin 2. Pin 3 GND must be connected to GND pin of CSI-C-12 input channel
